        "parameters": {
          "content": "## SYS 06 — LinkedIn Content Pipeline\n\n**Trigger:** Daily 6AM EST (cron).\n\n**What it does:** Fetches RSS feeds (TechCrunch AI, VentureBeat AI, HN Best), parses and filters to recent stories, uses Claude to generate a LinkedIn post (hook, full post, hashtags) per story, and appends drafts to the LinkedIn sheet for review. Optional approval flow or manual publish. Keeps a queue of on-brand, timely content.\n\n**Dependencies:** CONFIG, Call Claude API, Google Sheets (LinkedIn tab), optional Google Chat for approval.",
          "height": 320,
          "width": 460,
          "color": 5
        },
